data.description: Welcome to Trailwoods neighborhood that features walking trails, a splash pad, multiple playgrounds, picnic areas, pond and sports fields.  10 minutes from OU campus! Easy access to I-35, tons of shopping, and restaurants!  This delightful home offers open living concept, split bedroom plan, spacious bedrooms and closets.  Enjoy a covered back patio and a easily maintained backyard.  Home features a new roof, guttering, and garage door.  Welcome home to Trailwoods!!!
